@startuml
state ChooseAmount as "Choose/Enter Withdrawal Amount"
state PredefinedAmounts as "Predefined Amounts Selection"
state CustomAmount as "Custom Withdrawal Amount Input"
state CancelTransaction as "Cancel Transaction Option"
state StopTransaction as "Stop Transaction"
state ReturnCard as "Return Card"

ChooseAmount --> PredefinedAmounts : predefined amounts selection
ChooseAmount --> CustomAmount : custom amount input
PredefinedAmounts --> ChooseAmount
CustomAmount --> ChooseAmount
ChooseAmount --> CancelTransaction : transaction cancellation option
CancelTransaction --> StopTransaction : transaction cancelled
StopTransaction --> ReturnCard : card returned
ReturnCard --> [*]
@enduml
